  ## href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonRDS/latest/UserGuide/CHAP_PostgreSQL.html#PostgreSQL.Concepts.General.DBVersions">Supported PostgreSQL Database Versions</a> in the <i>Amazon RDS User Guide.</i> </p>
